title: Awesome Demon Teemo Skin made by Sirhaian'Arts

embed.description: WIP version of our League Community Project: Demon Teemo! All feedback is greatly welcome!

body:
What do you guys think about it ? Sirhaian has definitely put in some time and hard work on it. 

Make sure to leave a comment and like the video! :)

replies.body: This looks so professional, and despite hating Teeto, I love it. I like that it's a 'cute' demon concept, which fits with his overall style
